32:48.720 --> 32:52.560
or because he has a look on the statistics page,

32:52.560 --> 32:55.320
he says, OK, so I will do that.

32:55.320 --> 32:58.760
So he sends a mail with an address saying that, OK,

32:58.760 --> 33:03.840
this page, this description, this profile, I will translate it.

33:03.840 --> 33:05.120
So there is a mail.

33:05.120 --> 33:07.160
