33:26.080 --> 33:28.440
according to the number of mistakes

33:28.440 --> 33:31.080
which needs to be fixed, et cetera.

33:31.080 --> 33:35.360
And at the end, he says, OK, last chance for change.

33:35.360 --> 33:38.560
So OK, it's the last chance for you to review and to tell me

33:38.560 --> 33:40.120
if there is a problem.

33:40.120 --> 33:43.280
