33:43.280 --> 33:47.480
team, if there is not any reply, well, OK,

33:47.480 --> 33:50.360
the translator can either report a bug

33:50.360 --> 33:52.560
to say to the maintainer of the package, OK,

33:52.560 --> 33:53.760
there is a new translation.

33:53.760 --> 33:54.840
It's updates.

33:54.840 --> 33:57.040
